      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Coffee"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "We found an adorable French coffee shop to have a pastry and coffee on a rainy day. La Fiancee served great coffee options, breakfast items, and baked goods."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "image",
